| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0903 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6bef9eb3-adce-5d2f-be71-d847f258a5d4"
